Title: Geberit Pluvia HDPE clamp for steel square pipe
Description: This Geberit Pluvia support rail suspension element for square pipe is made of steel with a galvanised finish. It is used to fasten Geberit Pluvia support rails with square profiles and can be used for fastening pipes to ceilings.

Title: Geberit Pluvia HDPE wedge for guide bracket
Description: This Geberit Pluvia 90mm tension wedge is made of steel with a galvanised finish. It is used to fasten Geberit Pluvia pipe brackets, Pluvia support rail suspension elements and Pluvia connection elements to Pluvia support rails with square profiles.
category: Drainage/Rainwater, Floor and Roof Drains/Roof Drainage Accessories/Roof Drainage Accessories.csv -> Geberit Pluvia HDPE wedge for guide bracket

Title: Harmer screw with PVC adaptor 100mm 4"
Description: This Harmer 4" or 100mm threaded spigot adapter allows for the connections of a Harmer roof AV and detail threaded aluminium rainwater outlets to any pipe system. A cost-effective alternative to using a short length of steel gas tube to BS EN 10255 in cast iron socketed or socketless systems, this ABS adapter is supplied in a 400mm length and is taper threaded externally at one end to BS EN 10226-1 and chamfered at the other end to BS 4514 and BS EN 1329-1 spigot dimensions.
category: Drainage/Rainwater, Floor and Roof Drains/Roof Drainage Accessories/Roof Drainage Accessories.csv -> Harmer screw with PVC adaptor 100mm 4"

Title: Geberit Pluvia roof outlet with fastening flange for roof foils 12ltr/s
Description: Made of CrNi steel, this Geberit Pluvia roof outlet with 56mm fastening flange for roof foils is designed for use with the Geberit Pluvia siphonic roof drainage system.
